products.title: Butternut Cocoa Chili
products.description:
Rich, flavorful, and super comforting, this chili hits all the right notes of being satisfying while totally bean-free. The hint of sweetness from the butternut squash balances out the mild heat of the chili spices - it's a perfect balance. Pair it with freshly sliced avocado, guacamole, or sour cream to make this bowl even more hearty and satisfying! This meal is adapted from a reader-favorite recipe in Diane's first book, Practical Paleo.

INGREDIENTS: beef, tomatoes (tomatoes, tomato puree, salt, citric acid - may contain calcium chloride), butternut squash, bell peppers, onion, garlic, coconut oil, chili powder, unsweetened cocoa powder, cinnamon, smoked paprika, chipotle powder, cumin, salt.

Calories 440 | Carbs 20g | Protein 29g | Fat 28g | Fiber 6g
